# Application Icon

## Required
An `Icon.png` file is required for packaging the application with Fyne.

## Specifications
- **Format**: PNG
- **Size**: 512x512 pixels (will be automatically scaled for different uses)
- **Content**: Should represent MTGA Companion
- **Background**: Preferably transparent
- **Style**: Simple, recognizable icon that works at small sizes

## Where It's Used
- Application window title bar (16x16, 32x32)
- Taskbar/Dock (varies by platform)
- App switcher (Alt+Tab / Cmd+Tab)
- Desktop shortcuts
- macOS .app bundle
- Windows .exe resource

## Creation Options

### Option 1: Design Tool
Use a design tool like:
- Figma (free, web-based)
- Inkscape (free, open-source)
- Adobe Illustrator
- Sketch (macOS)

### Option 2: Icon Generator
Use an online icon generator:
- https://www.favicon-generator.org/
- https://realfavicongenerator.net/
- https://iconifier.net/

### Option 3: Commission
Commission a designer on:
- Fiverr
- Upwork
- 99designs

## Suggested Design Elements
- MTG mana symbols (if permitted by WotC)
- Cards or card back silhouette
- Arena logo elements (simplified)
- Data/statistics visual (graphs, charts)
- Companion/assistant theme

## Legal Considerations
- Do not copy official MTG/Arena artwork
- Ensure any assets used are licensed for commercial use
- Keep design simple to avoid trademark issues

## Placeholder
Until a proper icon is created, Fyne will use a default icon.
The application will still function correctly without a custom icon.

